{"word":"αἰθύσσω","slug":"αἰθύσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αἰθύσσω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αἴθω'><el>αἴθω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to put in rapid motion, stir up, kindle</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to quiver</i>, of leaves, <b><a href='S:Sappho Lyrica'>Sapph.</a></b><p/>"}]}